column4: I actually had to google to make sure it actually existed and it wasn't just the artists trying to cram as many cakes into one.
Someone just took choux pastry and just made it... very loooooong
It's super basic... but damn it does taste good.
How... how do you eat this thing?
Looks like it's been plucked out of an infinitely large cake
Bread... salt... Germans have the best naming.
Everyone likes the flan. Even if you don't like the taste, you have to admit it rocks... like literally... it rocks back and forth
